                        <item xml:id="e1">- On the incipit page (fol. 1), a chain of black and red
                           dot asterisks is placed in the upper margin. &#xD; - The scribe used
                           compressed script: <locus target="#31va">31va</locus>.&#xD; -
                           Tamallas-sign, in the shape of a cross (+), indicating the place where
                           the omissions, written in the upper margin, belong: <locus target="#4vb">4vb</locus>, 19ra, 33rb, 40vb, 46va.&#xD; - Tamallas-sign, in the
                           shape of two perpendicular lines (┴), indicating the place where the
                           omissions, written in the upper margin, belong: <locus target="#49vc">49vc</locus>, 50ra, 53ra, 65vc.&#xD; - Tamallas-sign, in the shape of
                           two perpendicular lines (├), indicating the place where the omissions,
                           written in the upper margin, belong: <locus target="#120ra">120ra</locus>.&#xD; - Many omitted letters or words inserted
                           interlineally: e.g., <locus target="#3rb">3rb</locus>, 3va, 4rc, 4va,
                           5vb, 6vb, 8ra, 9ra, 26rc, 48vb, 51va, 61vb.&#xD; - Omitted words added at
                           the beginning of the line: <locus target="#16va">16va</locus>, 49ra,
                           58ra, 66va, 69va, 70va, 86ra.&#xD; - Omitted words added at the end of
                           the line: <locus target="#66vc">66vc</locus>, 71vc, 72vc.&#xD; - Many
                           corrections written over erasures: e.g., <locus target="#2va">2va</locus>, 13rc, 16vc, 22rc, 27va, 34vc, 78vc.&#xD; - Erasures marked
                           with thin black lines: <locus target="#6va">6va</locus>, 13ra, 33vc,
                           70vb, 86ra, 86vb, 119ra, 156vb.&#xD; - Many immediate corrections
